    tr(elem = 'row')
      td
        a(href = '#')
          img(src = '../images/c-max_mirror.jpg')
      td(elem = 'titles')
        h3(elem = 'title', mix = 'block:compact-text'): a(elem = 'link', href = '#'): b C-MAX Зеркало левое с регулировочным мотором
        h5(elem = 'subtitle') Depo, 431-1176LMLD-EM
      td Тайвань
      td
        p(block = 'product-status', mod = 'is:available') В магазине 6 шт.
        button(block = 'button', mod = 'type:buy,size:small')
          i.icon(block = 'icon', elem = 'buy')
          | Купить
      td(elem = 'price') 83<span class="thsp"></span>500 <span class="r">руб.</span>
